[[Image:American Mushroom Institute logo.gif|thumb|right|200px|Logo of the American Mushroom Institute.]]
The '''American Mushroom Institute''' is the [[industry trade group]] for the [[United States|U.S.]] [[mushroom]] industry.

In 2007 the Institute commissioned Chester County, Pa., author [[Bruce Mowday]] to compile a photographic history of the local industry. ''Chester County Mushroom Farming'' (Arcadia) was published in 2008. 

