'''Electricité du Liban''' (Electricity of Lebanon – EDL) is the main Lebanese electricity producer. It was founded by Decree No. 16878 dated July 10, 1964, and mandated the responsibility of the generation, transmission, and distribution of electrical energy in Lebanon.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.edl.gov.lb/AboutEDL.htm|title=About EDL|website=Edl.gov.lb|accessdate=2017-07-29}}</ref>

