[[File:Gloucester Business Park (geograph 3283269).jpg|thumb|Gloucester Business Park]] '''Gloucester Business Park''' is a [[business park]] situated in [[Hucclecote]] on the outskirts of [[Gloucester]], [[England]] with close links to the [[M5_motorway|M5]] and [[A417 road|A417]].
Current residents of the business park include [[Direct Wines]], [[Horizon Nuclear Power]], [[Fortis (finance)|Ageas]], [[National_Health_Service_%28England%29|NHS]] and [[Detica]].<ref>{{ cite web |url=http://www.gloucesterbusinesspark.co.uk/occupiers/overview.html |title=Occupiers in Gloucester Business Park |accessdate=2010-07-26}}</ref>
In 2009 the business park won an award from the British Association of Landscape Industries.<ref>{{ cite web |url=http://www.bali.org.uk/awards/2009/winners#award_50 |title=BALI 2009 Awards |accessdate=2010-07-28}}</ref>
