'''Independent Industrialists and Businessmen Association''' ({{lang-tr|Müstakil Sanayici ve İşadamları Derneği}}, '''MÜSİAD'''), is a [[non-governmental organization]] .According to 2015 records, MÜSİAD has 85 contact points in Turkey, 159 contact points in 63 different countries, and more than 11,000 members. The association holds an [[ISO 9001:2000]] Quality Certificate.
MÜSİAD organizes an annual [[defense industry]] fair called ''High-Tech Port by MÜSİAD''. The second fair was held between 6–8 October 2015 in [[Doha]], [[Qatar]], and promoted billions of dollars of trade between Turkey and Qatar.<ref>[http://www.qfc.qa/news-and-events/Pages/2nd-High-Tech-Port-Fair-and-19th-IBF-Congress.aspx 2nd High Tech Port Fair & 19th International Business Forum (IBF) Congress (By invitation only)]</ref><ref>[http://www.dailysabah.com/money/2015/09/30/turkish-defense-industry-aims-to-sign-deals-worth-5b-in-qatar Turkish defense industry aims to sign deals worth $5B in Qatar]</ref> MÜSİAD also supports Turkey’s [[Housing Developers and Investors Organization]] (KONUTDER) exhibitions to increase [[real estate]] trade ties to investors from the [[Persian Gulf|Gulf]].<ref>[http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/housing-sector-representatives-set-to-host-gulf-investors-in-istanbul.aspx?pageID=238&nID=88837&NewsCatID=345 Housing sector representatives set to host Gulf investors in Istanbul]</ref>
